<div class="heading resPageHeading">


























<h1 >Report a Near Miss or Hazard</h1></div>

<div class="content stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="92cff801-d868-4103-b140-7a21518d53a0" >

    <p>A hazard is an object or situation with the potential to cause harm to a person or to Ryerson property. A near miss is an unplanned event that has the potential to cause a leak, spill, explosion, release or unexpected contact with a chemical/substance/object that did not result in an incident or injury/illness.</p> 
<p>Reporting near misses and hazards are important as it allows changes to be implemented to prevent future incidents and injuries from occurring. This includes but is not limited to:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>the reporting of unsafe working conditions or habits;&nbsp;</li> 
 <li>improper use of or malfunctioning equipment; and/or</li> 
 <li>hazardous emissions or the detection of such.&nbsp;</li> 
</ul> 
<p>It is everyone’s responsibility to report and correct these hazards immediately in order to prevent an incident or injury from occurring.</p> 
<h2>Imminent hazards</h2> 
<p>Imminent hazards have the potential for causing <strong>serious and immediate</strong> injuries or property damage. Examples of such hazards include exposed electrical wires, major chemical spills generating dangerous fumes, machine guarding removed from a piece of equipment, or an exposed open manhole.</p> 
<h2>What the employee should do</h2> 
<p>If you are an employee who has identified an imminent hazard, follow these steps:</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#92cff801-d868-4103-b140-7a21518d53a0");});</script></div>

				

				
				<div class="resAccordion section">
























 


<div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
        <div class="panel-group accordion background-hidden" id="6353fe71-3c98-4cf2-831e-fa2539b0f4bc" role="tablist" aria-multiselectable="true">
			
				<div class="resAccordionControl" role="group" aria-label="Accordion Actions">
					<button class="resAccordionOpenAll">Open All</button> <button class="resAccordionCloseAll">Close All</button>
				</div>
				<script type="text/javascript">$(document).ready(function(){ initResAccordionControl("6353fe71-3c98-4cf2-831e-fa2539b0f4bc", false); });</script>
			
            
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <!-- Accordion Heading -->
                <div class="panel-heading container-clipboard">
                    <h3 class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1505235400100-step-1--isolate-the-hazard" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#" href="#accordion-content-1505235400100-step-1--isolate-the-hazard" aria-controls="accordion-content-1505235400100-step-1--isolate-the-hazard" aria-expanded="false">
                            Step 1: Isolate the hazard
                        </a>
                    </h3>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1505235400100-step-1--isolate-the-hazard" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1505235400100-step-1--isolate-the-hazard">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1505235400100 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="a0f557a6-ca98-42d8-aef6-f1478d86300a" >

    <p><strong>Only if it is safe to do so</strong>, immediately shut down or turn off the equipment, close the door, and quickly and calmly leave the area along with any other occupants. Place caution tape on the door to prevent unauthorized access during the investigation.</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#a0f557a6-ca98-42d8-aef6-f1478d86300a");});</script></div>

				</div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <!-- Accordion Heading -->
                <div class="panel-heading container-clipboard">
                    <h3 class="panel-title">
