    <h4>Hazards related to laboratories, fire safety or ergonomics</h4> 
<p>For hazards related to laboratories, fire safety or ergonomics (e.g. chemical, radiation, X-ray and laser safety; minor spills and waste disposal; fire safety, equipment malfunctions; and/or ergonomic hazards) please contact Environmental Health and Safety at&nbsp;<a href="mailto:ehs@ryerson.ca">ehs@ryerson.ca</a>&nbsp;or 416-979-5000, ext. 553770.</p> 
<h4>Hazards related to facilities and building maintenance</h4> 
<p>For hazards related to facilities and building maintenance (e.g. non-hazardous spills, temperature variances, repairs or maintenance, fire extinguisher maintenance, pest control, non-toxic waste-related issues and/or asbestos) please contact the&nbsp;FMD Help Desk at&nbsp;<a href="mailto:fixit@ryerson.ca">fixit@ryerson.ca</a>&nbsp;or 416-979-5091.</p>
    





